(185, 'Native English Online Sales', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', '0', 'Kremsoft', 'N/A', 'This is a great opportunity to join an innovative, enthusiastic, team of exceptional of creative marketers <br /><br />and reporting directly to our CEO, a genius marketer! Develop your skills and learn new techniques <br /><br />working with interesting clients in Content & Social Marketing.<br /><br /> Email Marketing<br /><br /> Direct Marketing<br /><br /> Telemarketing<br /><br /> Social Media Marketing<br /><br /> Business to Business sales<br /><br /> CRM Knowledge<br /><br />This is a very dynamic role in a rapidly growing company. <br /><br />Training is provided but creativity is a must. Competitive salary and excellent bonuses available', '0', '2018-03-16 00:05:54', '2018-03-16 00:05:54'),
